1.SIMPLE SCREEN RECORDER
$ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:maarten-baert/simplescreenrecorder
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install simplescreenrecorder
!!!!!!error solution:-
sudo su 
cd /etc/gdm3
nano custom.conf
remove comment from the tag 
#WaylandEnable=false
to
WaylandEnable=false
and then save it 
black screen recording solve
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Website:--https://linuxhint.com/install_simple_screen_recorder_ubuntu/
